  "type": "PrimaryTheme",
  "number": 8219,
  "title": "courage",
  "comment": "The quality of being able to act bravely under difficulties or in the face of opposition; being prepared to do dangerous or risky things in obedience to God, in the belief that he will strengthen, guard and protect his people.",
